---
title: Smokey Chicken Drumsticks & Cheesy Rainbow Veg with Truffle Mayonnaise & Roasted Almonds
description: Tried and true chicken and veg just had a major makeover! This chicken is marinated in Kiwi seasoning and honey for a sweet
and smokey hit, and is accompanied by a rainbow of roasted veggies. A dollop of creamy Italian truffle mayo is the perfect
addition to tie it all together.

